name: Æi x Ternum 1251 - ERROR CODE
description: Rejected the first time round, she is back displaying a new message - EXTERNAL FATAL ERROR.  This Æi x Ternum 1251 is about to deploy her defensive weapon.   Original text: ‘Second model in ‘The Satisfaction of Desire’ Hic et Nunc  XIII series. Æi x Ternum 1251 smart, beautiful and equip with the ‘Love Bomb’; defensive Æi-x-Tillery.’
